qucsrflayout (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  [ Added ]
  * Supports Linux.
  * Supports Windows (Benjamin Vernoux <https://github.com/bvernoux>).
  * Requires Qucs installed.
  * Supports QucsStudio schematics if Qucs is installed too.
  * Supports output formats :
    * .kicad_pcb : KiCad board
    * .kicad_mod : KiCad module
    * .lht : pcb-rnd board
  * Supports microstrip components :
    * MCORN
    * MCOUPLED
    * MCROSS
    * MGAP
    * MLIN
    * MMBEND
    * MOPEN
    * MRSTUB
    * MSTEP
    * MTEE
    * MVIA
    * Pac

 -- Thomas Lepoix <thomas.lepoix@protonmail.ch>  Fri, 14 Feb 2020 00:00:00 +0100
